An AI-powered **multi-agent event planning system** built with [CrewAI](https://github.com/joaomdmoura/crewai) and [Streamlit](https://streamlit.io/). This application demonstrates how specialized AI agents can collaborate to plan, manage, and review events with structured workflows and user feedback.

